I know. I just wanted to know who he was,you know?
我知道啊 只是想知道他是谁而已

172
00:11:00,92 --> 00:11:02,35
Yeah,I know.
是啊，我知道

173
00:11:05,13 --> 00:11:09,15
I wasn't completely honest with you when I said I didn't know...
我说我不知道他住在哪里…

174
00:11:09,36 --> 00:11:11,59
...exactly where he lived.
…是有点骗你

175
00:11:11,93 --> 00:11:13,56
What do you mean?
什么意思？

176
00:11:13,77 --> 00:11:17,80
He lives at 74 Laurel Drive in Middletown.
他住在米德城罗瑞街74号

177
00:11:20,14 --> 00:11:22,70
If you hit the Dairy Queen, you've gone too far.
要是看到黛莉冰淇淋就过头了

178
00:11:22,91 --> 00:11:24,78
You can take my cab.
开我的车去吧

179
00:11:26,78 --> 00:11:27,77
Thank you.
谢了

180
00:11:29,32 --> 00:11:32,72
-Nobody else drives that cab. -Got it.
我的计程车别让别人开啊 知道了

181
00:11:34,32 --> 00:11:36,38
I'm gonna see my dad!
我要见到我爸爸了

182
00:11:36,96 --> 00:11:37,89
Thank you.
谢谢

183
00:11:41,60 --> 00:11:43,22
Wish me luck,Grandpa.
好吧，祝我好运了，爷爷

184
00:11:52,81 --> 00:11:54,43
Phoebe here with the cab yet?
菲比开计程车来了吗？

185
00:11:54,64 --> 00:11:56,77
Yeah,she brought the invisible cab.
来了，那是一辆隐形车

186
00:11:56,98 --> 00:11:58,21
Hop in!
上车吧

187
00:11:59,08 --> 00:12:01,74
She'd better get here. The stores close at 7.
她最好快一点 服饰店七点就关门了

188
00:12:01,95 --> 00:12:04,75
It'll be two hours to Phoebe's dad's house...
安啦，我想菲比去她爸那儿 大概两个小时…

189
00:12:04,95 --> 00:12:07,05
...they'll meet,chat, swap life stories.
…他们见面，聊天 交换生活故事

190
00:12:07,25 --> 00:12:08,95
We'll have plenty of time.
还有很多时间的

191
00:12:10,46 --> 00:12:12,32
Hey,here she comes!
她来了

192
00:12:20,84 --> 00:12:21,96
Can you believe this?
你们相信吗？

193
00:12:22,34 --> 00:12:25,27
In,like,two hours I'm gonna have a dad.
再两个小时我就有爸爸了

194
00:12:26,41 --> 00:12:27,81
Yeah,big stuff!
是呀，大事哦

195
00:12:28,18 --> 00:12:29,47
Okay,let's go!
对呀，走吧

196
00:12:29,68 --> 00:12:31,65
Here,you have to hold this.
好，你来拿着这个

197
00:12:35,12 --> 00:12:37,02
"Brake,left. Gas,right"?
左刹车，右加速？

198
00:12:37,95 --> 00:12:39,28
That's my cheat sheet.
对，我的小抄

199
00:12:43,16 --> 00:12:45,96
-Where's my seat belt? -There isn't one.
安全带呢？ 你那边没有了

200
00:12:46,19 --> 00:12:48,46
The paramedics had to cut through it.
被救护人员剪开了

201
00:13:00,61 --> 00:13:03,44
Come on,just tell me. Please,please!
告诉我嘛，拜托…

202
00:13:03,71 --> 00:13:07,61
For the 16th time: No,I do not think you're obsessive!
这是第十六次了： 不，我不认为你钻牛角尖

203
00:13:09,45 --> 00:13:12,21
-It's hot in here! -Rach,get the heat.
天哪，这里怎么这么热啊 麻烦把暖气关小

204
00:13:12,45 --> 00:13:14,68
Ross,turn the heat down,please?
罗斯，把暖气关小

205
00:13:15,19 --> 00:13:17,35
The difference between obsessive
两个之间是有差别…

206
00:13:17,63 --> 00:13:18,68
Ross,the heat!
罗斯，暖气

207
00:13:18,89 --> 00:13:22,85
Okay! Heat,heat,heat! And I'm the obsessive one?
好，暖气…还说我钻牛角尖？

208
00:13:25,13 --> 00:13:27,03
This way is on.
好吧，往这边是开

209
00:13:27,23 --> 00:13:29,50
So this is...
往这边是…

210
00:13:32,07 --> 00:13:33,13
...off.
…关

211
00:13:34,81 --> 00:13:37,00
Did you just break the radiator?
你是否把暖气机弄坏了？

212
00:13:37,21 --> 00:13:39,91
No,I was turning the knob and...
没有，我不过是转了开关…

213
00:13:40,31 --> 00:13:41,84
... here it is.
…结果就掉了

214
00:13:42,58 --> 00:13:44,52
Well,put it back!
那就装回去啊

215
00:13:47,72 --> 00:13:49,42
It won't go back.
装不回去了

216
00:13:49,66 --> 00:13:50,72
I'll call the super.
我打电话给管理员

217
00:13:50,99 --> 00:13:52,32
Here,let me try.
来，我来试试

218
00:13:52,53 --> 00:13:55,98
That's right. I forgot about your ability to fuse metal.
对了 我忘了你融合金属的能力了

219
00:13:57,06 --> 00:13:58,73
Hey,it's Funny's cousin...
好笑的相反…

220
00:13:58,93 --> 00:13:59,99
... Not Funny!
…不好笑

221
00:14:00,50 --> 00:14:01,76
Hi,Mr. Treeger?
崔先生？

222
00:14:02,00 --> 00:14:03,90
It's Rachel Greene from upstairs.
我是楼上的林瑞秋

223
00:14:04,17 --> 00:14:07,20
Yes,somebody broke our knob on the radiator...
对，有人弄坏 我们暖气的开关了…

224
00:14:07,41 --> 00:14:09,77
...and it's really hot in here.
…我们这里好热

225
00:14:10,85 --> 00:14:13,41
Yes,it's hot enough to bake cookies.
对，热到可以烤饼干了

226
00:14:16,02 --> 00:14:18,35
Could we have a new one by 6?
你想你能在六点以前换好吗？

227
00:14:19,12 --> 00:14:21,45
Tuesday? We can't wait until Tuesday.
什么？不，不，星期二 我们等不到那个时候

228
00:14:21,72 --> 00:14:23,28
We're having a party tonight.
我们今晚有派对

229
00:14:23,52 --> 00:14:25,01
Okay,tip the man.
好吧，给他小费

230
00:14:25,23 --> 00:14:27,52
If he doesn't like our cookies,too bad.
不，不喜欢 我们的饼干就算了吧

231
00:14:27,73 --> 00:14:28,96
I won't be blackmailed.
我才不要任人勒索呢

232
00:14:29,23 --> 00:14:31,46
Look,if it gets a little warm...
这里有点热…

233
00:14:31,77 --> 00:14:33,39
...it can be a theme party.
…就改成主题派对好了

234
00:14:33,63 --> 00:14:36,40
Here's a theme: "Come on in,live like bacon!"
这下有主题了： “请进，像热窝上的蚂蚁吧”

235
00:14:39,64 --> 00:14:40,80
This is it!
就是这里了

236
00:14:41,11 --> 00:14:42,13
Seventy-four.
74号

237
00:14:44,65 --> 00:14:46,88
So that's what this is for!
长途跋涉为这个

238
00:14:48,38 --> 00:14:51,04
This is it. I'm gonna meet my dad.
就是这里了 我要见到我爸爸了

239
00:14:51,45 --> 00:14:53,61
This is like the biggest thing ever.
这真是前所未有的大事

240
00:14:54,39 --> 00:14:55,86
Sure is.
说得没错

241
00:14:56,06 --> 00:14:57,72
Here I go. I'm going in.
好了，我要进去了

242
00:14:57,96 --> 00:14:58,79
All right!
好啊

243
00:14:59,06 --> 00:15:00,65
Good luck,Pheebs.
一切顺利哦

244
00:15:02,40 --> 00:15:03,95
Here I go.
好了，我走了

245
00:15:05,83 --> 00:15:07,32
Here I go.
我走了

246
00:15:09,07 --> 00:15:10,47
I'm going.
我要走了

247
00:15:23,92 --> 00:15:26,48
Welcome to our tropical Christmas party.
欢迎光临我们的热带圣诞派对

248
00:15:26,75 --> 00:15:30,25
Put your coats,sweaters, pants and shirts in the bedroom.
外套，毛衣，长裤跟衬衫 请放在卧室里面

249
00:15:32,76 --> 00:15:35,19
It's hard to tell because I'm sweating...
我在冒汗，所以看不出来…

250
00:15:35,43 --> 00:15:38,46
... but I use exactly what the gel bottle says.
…但我完全遵照 瓶上指示的用量

251
00:15:40,94 --> 00:15:45,34
An amount about the size of a pea. How can that be too much?
一颗豆子大小的份量而已 那怎么会太多呢？

252
00:15:48,14 --> 00:15:49,27
Ice?
冰块？

253
00:15:49,88 --> 00:15:53,37
Ice? Ice squares anyone? Take a napkin.
谁要冰块？拿张餐巾

254
00:15:55,55 --> 00:15:56,78
Monica!
摩妮卡？摩妮卡？

255
00:15:58,45 --> 00:16:00,94
Your guests are turning into jerky.
你的客人都快变成人干了

256
00:16:01,16 --> 00:16:03,32
Really? I'm perfectly comfortable.
真的？我觉得舒服得很

257
00:16:04,12 --> 00:16:06,62
Hey! Get in line,buddy. I was next.
排队呀，兄弟，换我了

258
00:16:11,17 --> 00:16:12,36
Mr. Treeger.
崔先生

259
00:16:12,70 --> 00:16:14,13
You said there was a party.
你说有派对啊？

260
00:16:15,84 --> 00:16:18,00
Well,hey,welcome to our sauna.
欢迎光临三温暖

261
00:16:18,24 --> 00:16:21,37
Is it hot? My body always stays cool.
很热吗？我从来不觉得热

262
00:16:21,64 --> 00:16:23,84
Probably because I have so much skin.
说不定是因为我皮肤多了

263
00:16:25,08 --> 00:16:26,74
Hey,cheese!
起士

264
00:16:28,52 --> 00:16:31,18
Here's the chance. Monica,give him cash.
好吧，好吧，机会来了 摩妮卡，给他现金

265
00:16:31,39 --> 00:16:34,51
Rachel,give him your earrings. Something. Anything!
瑞秋，把你的耳环给他 快啊，任何东西都给他

266
00:16:34,72 --> 00:16:36,31
No,I will not cave.
不，我不屈服

267
00:16:36,52 --> 00:16:37,42
I'm with Mon.
对，我也是

268
00:16:37,66 --> 00:16:40,99
All right. You know how you say I never seize the day?
好吧… 你说我从不把握机会？

269
00:16:41,23 --> 00:16:44,53
Even though he's your super, I'm seizing.
他虽然是你们的管理员 我也要把握一下

270
00:16:46,43 --> 00:16:47,70
Mr. Treeger?
崔先生？

271
00:16:48,94 --> 00:16:51,53
Here is $50. Merry Christmas.
这里是50块钱，圣诞快乐

272
00:16:53,11 --> 00:16:54,90
I didn't get you anything.
我没有准备你的礼物

273
00:16:55,58 --> 00:16:57,20
Here's five back.
送你5块钱好了

274
00:16:58,35 --> 00:17:01,11
No,that's your Christmas tip.
不，那是你的圣诞红包

275
00:17:01,35 --> 00:17:05,88
Do you think there's a chance you can fix that radiator now?
你认为你可不可以 现在把暖气给修好？

276
00:17:06,09 --> 00:17:08,25
No can do. Like I told the girl...
没办法，我已经说过了…

277
00:17:08,56 --> 00:17:10,28
... I can't get a knob until Tuesday.
…星期二才拿得到新的开关

278
00:17:11,16 --> 00:17:12,09
Ross?
罗斯？

279
00:17:12,93 --> 00:17:14,59
He's playing baseball.
看来他很僵硬哦

280
00:17:14,80 --> 00:17:16,42
You mean hardball?
你要说强硬吗？

281
00:17:20,03 --> 00:17:21,06
Whatever.
随便啦

282
00:17:21,87 --> 00:17:22,89
What you gonna do?
你打算怎么样呢？

283
00:17:23,10 --> 00:17:25,23
Excuse me. I'm seizing.
抱歉，我要把握一下

284
00:17:25,44 --> 00:17:26,70
Mr. Treeger?
崔先生？

285
00:17:28,08 --> 00:17:29,60
Here's another 50.
我再给你五十

286
00:17:30,08 --> 00:17:31,31
Happy Hanukkah.
祝你圣诞节快乐

287
00:17:31,81 --> 00:17:34,91
Will this help with the knob-getting?
这样我们是不是 可以拿到新的开关了呢？

288
00:17:36,48 --> 00:17:39,15
No,the place is not open till Tuesday.
不行 那家店星期二才会开门

289
00:17:39,82 --> 00:17:41,81
Am I not saying it right?
我的发音不标准吗？

290
00:17:43,26 --> 00:17:45,66
So you really did like my cookies?
你真的喜欢我的饼干吗？

291
00:17:45,89 --> 00:17:49,66
Yeah,they were so personal. It really showed you cared.
是呀，那好温暖哦 真的表示你的关心

292
00:17:55,24 --> 00:17:56,90
Nice seizing...
把握得好…

293
00:17:57,14 --> 00:17:58,73
...gel boy.
…发胶兄

294
00:18:03,41 --> 00:18:05,34
Is this mistletoe?
这是w寄生，没错吧？

295
00:18:07,35 --> 00:18:08,97
No,that....
不，那个叫…

296
00:18:09,25 --> 00:18:11,01
That is basil.
…叫九层塔

297
00:18:14,79 --> 00:18:17,81
If it was mistletoe, I was gonna kiss you.
如果是w寄生，我就要亲你了

298
00:18:20,13 --> 00:18:21,75
No,it's still basil.
不，那还是九层塔

299
00:18:24,36 --> 00:18:28,96
Chestnuts roasting on an open fire
火炉上烤栗子

300
00:18:31,31 --> 00:18:35,21
Jack Frost nipping at your nose
雪人在啃你的鼻子

301
00:18:37,71 --> 00:18:39,44
-How far did you get? -Mailbox.
你走到哪里啊？ 信箱

302
00:18:39,65 --> 00:18:42,31
All right,we're getting closer.
有进步了

303
00:18:44,12 --> 00:18:45,28
What's going on?
菲比，你怎么了？

304
00:18:46,15 --> 00:18:48,82
It's just like a whole mess of stuff.
其实原因很多啦

305
00:18:49,06 --> 00:18:53,62
Like yesterday,my dad was this famous Burma tree-surgeon guy.
昨天，我爸爸他还是一个 名闻遐迩的缅甸树医

306
00:18:53,86 --> 00:18:57,30
And you know,now he's a pharmacist guy and....
可是他现在 却变成一个药剂师了…

307
00:18:57,50 --> 00:19:01,63
Well,maybe he's this really cool pharmacist guy.
或许他是一个 很酷的药剂师也说不定

308
00:19:01,87 --> 00:19:05,70
Yeah,maybe! And I'll knock on the door...
对，或许，对 然后我会跑去敲他的门…

309
00:19:06,37 --> 00:19:09,64
...and he'll hug me, and I'll have a dad!
…他会拥抱我，我会有个爸爸

310
00:19:09,88 --> 00:19:13,51
I'll go to his pharmacy and everyone will be nice to me...
然后大家都会亲切地对待我…

311
00:19:13,75 --> 00:19:16,55
... because,you know, I'm Frank's daughter.
…因为我是法兰的女儿

312
00:19:16,75 --> 00:19:18,15
So why not go knock?
那就快去敲门哪

313
00:19:21,99 --> 00:19:26,76
Because,I mean,what if he's not this great-dad guy?
因为如果他没有那么棒呢？

314
00:19:27,59 --> 00:19:32,19
What if he's still the dirtbag who ran out on my mom and us?
如果他还是那个 抛妻弃子的浑球呢？

315
00:19:37,24 --> 00:19:38,60
You know what?
你知道吗？

316
00:19:39,27 --> 00:19:41,94
I've already lost a fake dad this week.
我这个礼拜 已经失去一个假爸爸了

317
00:19:43,51 --> 00:19:45,91
I don't think I'm ready to lose a real one.
我不想再失去一个真的爸爸

318
00:19:48,42 --> 00:19:52,11
Pheebs,that's okay. You took a big step today.
菲菲，没关系啦 你已经跨了一大步了

319
00:19:55,06 --> 00:19:58,58
Someday,when you're ready, you'll make it past the hedges.
有一天当你准备好的时候 你就会越过那片篱笆了

320
00:19:58,79 --> 00:20:01,63
And when you do, he'll be lucky to have you.
那个时候他会有幸得到你

321
00:20:02,70 --> 00:20:04,19
You guys....
你们…

322
00:20:08,40 --> 00:20:09,93
Sorry about your shopping.
抱歉，你们来不及购物了

323
00:20:10,14 --> 00:20:13,04
Oh,that's okay. We'll figure something out.
没关系，会有办法的

324
00:20:15,74 --> 00:20:17,94
I know you're not going in there...
我知道你不要进去…

325
00:20:18,15 --> 00:20:21,58
... but you think it's okay if I go in and use his bathroom?
…不过你想我可不可以进去 跟他借一下洗手间？

326
00:20:22,62 --> 00:20:24,48
That's fine,never mind.
没关系，算了

327
00:20:26,29 --> 00:20:27,78
Cool,snow!
酷耶，下雪了

328
00:20:27,99 --> 00:20:29,92
Kind of like a blank canvas.
像空白的画布

329
00:20:40,00 --> 00:20:43,09
Ho-ho-ho-holy crap, is it hot in here!
这里面好热啊

330
00:20:45,44 --> 00:20:47,50
You mind if I turn the heat down?
介意我把暖气关小吗？

331
00:20:47,74 --> 00:20:50,97
We could have used that kind of thinking earlier!
我们怎么都没想到呢

332
00:20:51,41 --> 00:20:53,07
So,Pheebs,how did it go?
菲菲，结果怎么样？

333
00:20:53,48 --> 00:20:55,64
Oh,I couldn't go in.
我没有办法进去

334
00:20:55,85 --> 00:20:57,82
-Honey,I'm sorry. -Are you okay?
好可惜喔 你还好吗？

335
00:20:58,02 --> 00:21:00,78
Yeah,it's okay, because I know he's there.
好，没关系 因为我知道他在哪儿

336
00:21:00,99 --> 00:21:02,92
So that's enough for now.
现在只要那样就够了

337
00:21:03,12 --> 00:21:06,29
Hey,it's after midnight! Merry Christmas,everyone!
各位，过了十二点了 祝大家圣诞快乐

338
00:21:06,49 --> 00:21:09,43
Oh,right! Merry Christmas!
圣诞快乐

339
00:21:11,63 --> 00:21:12,93
The knob was broken...
开关坏了…

340
00:21:13,13 --> 00:21:16,63
...so I turned it off from underneath. I hope that's all right.
…所以我从下面关掉了 希望不会有问题

341
00:21:28,35 --> 00:21:30,37
Rach,these are for you.
瑞秋，送你的

342
00:21:31,35 --> 00:21:32,88
Wiper blades!
汽车雨刷

343
00:21:33,65 --> 00:21:35,35
I don't even have a car.
我连车都没有

344
00:21:35,56 --> 00:21:39,65
No,but with this new-car smell, you'll think you do!
对呀，但加上这个芳香剂 你会以为你有

345
00:21:42,66 --> 00:21:44,65
Okay,Pheebs,your turn.
菲菲，换你了

346
00:21:48,77 --> 00:21:50,40
Toilet-seat covers!
马桶纸垫啊

347
00:21:53,54 --> 00:21:56,20
Is that what you did while I got gas?
我去加油的时候 你们就去买这个吗？

348
00:21:56,58 --> 00:21:58,24
You guys!
你们两个真好！

349
00:21:59,35 --> 00:22:00,44
And for Ross...
